sections.Trivia:
- Although this set of episodes makes up the ninth "Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story" series, the number 9 isn't used in the titles. The Wiki is using the "9" to help distinguish the set from the original Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story.
- In one of her two posters, the magician character Kira Miyahara has brown hair, while in The Séance's Double Locked Room Mystery Case‎‎ had orange hair.
- The names of the suspects come from the manga Attack on Titan by Hajime Isayama[1]:
Noriya Makabe (真壁 則也) comes from "Wall Maria" (ウォール・マリア, wall in Japanese is "kabe" (壁)), one of the walls keeping the "Titans" from the Humans;
Toshinari Shiga (志賀 敏成) comes from "Shiganshina district" (シガンシナ区), the hometown of the main characters;
Hiroto Yasutomi (安富 裕人) comes from "Trost district" (トロスト区 ,Torosuto-ku?);
Mika Shiga (志賀 美伽) comes from "Shiganshina district" and Mikasa Ackerman, one of the series' main characters.
